extends layout

block content
  div(class="min-h-screen flex flex-col")
    //- Header
    header(class="border-b border-gray-700 h-16 flex items-center px-6")
      div(class="max-w-4xl mx-auto w-full")
        a(href="/" class="font-semibold text-sm tracking-tight flex items-center gap-2")
          span(class="text-lg") ▲
          span InviteChat

    //- Main
    main(class="flex-1 py-16 px-6")
      div(class="max-w-2xl mx-auto")
        div(class="mb-12")
          p(class="text-gray-500 text-xs font-mono mb-3 uppercase tracking-wider") legal
          h1(class="text-2xl font-medium") Privacy Policy
          p(class="text-gray-500 text-sm mt-2") Last updated: January 2026
        
        div(class="space-y-10 text-sm text-gray-300 leading-relaxed")
          section
            h2(class="text-white font-medium mb-3 flex items-center gap-3")
              span(class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs") 01
              | Information We Collect
            p(class="mb-3") We collect the following information when you use our service:
            ul(class="space-y-1 text-gray-400 ml-6")
              li — Discord user ID, username, and avatar
              li — Telegram user ID and username
              li — Payment information (processed by Stripe)
          
          section
            h2(class="text-white font-medium mb-3 flex items-center gap-3")
              span(class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs") 02
              | How We Use Your Information
            p(class="mb-3") We use your information to:
            ul(class="space-y-1 text-gray-400 ml-6")
              li — Process payments and verify purchases
              li — Assign premium roles and generate invite links
              li — Communicate with you about your account
          
          section
            h2(class="text-white font-medium mb-3 flex items-center gap-3")
              span(class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs") 03
              | Data Storage and Security
            p Your data is stored securely and we implement appropriate technical measures to protect your information. Payment data is handled entirely by Stripe and we do not store credit card information.
          
          section
            h2(class="text-white font-medium mb-3 flex items-center gap-3")
              span(class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs") 04
              | Third-Party Services
            p(class="mb-3") We use the following third-party services:
            ul(class="space-y-1 text-gray-400 ml-6")
              li — Stripe for payment processing
              li — Discord for authentication and role management
              li — Telegram for authentication and group access
          
          section
            h2(class="text-white font-medium mb-3 flex items-center gap-3")
              span(class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs") 05
              | Data Sharing
            p We do not sell or share your personal information with third parties except as necessary to provide our services or as required by law.
          
          section
            h2(class="text-white font-medium mb-3 flex items-center gap-3")
              span(class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs") 06
              | Your Rights
            p(class="mb-3") You have the right to:
            ul(class="space-y-1 text-gray-400 ml-6")
              li — Access your personal data
              li — Request deletion of your data
              li — Opt out of marketing communications
          
          section
            h2(class="text-white font-medium mb-3 flex items-center gap-3")
              span(class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs") 07
              | Cookies
            p We use session cookies to maintain your login state. These are essential for the service to function and are not used for tracking.
          
          section
            h2(class="text-white font-medium mb-3 flex items-center gap-3")
              span(class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs") 08
              | Contact
            p For privacy-related questions, please contact us through our Discord server.
        
        div(class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-gray-700")
          a(href="/" class="text-gray-500 text-sm hover:text-white transition-colors") ← Back
